sourcesContent:
import React from 'react';
import {
  ProjectContainer, ProjectTitle, LinksContainer, GradientButton,
  Description, DemonstrationContainer, StepsContainer, StepItem,
  StepDescription, GifContainer, GifImage, Card, PillBadge,
  GradientBackground, CircleExpand, TextMod, GradientText,
  GradientContainer, AnimatedGradient, LineHeightText, HoverGradientShift,
  DashAnimatedLine, LinePulse, GlowingLine, GrowVerticalLine, GrowHorizontalLine,
  GlassCard, FloatingElement, ExpandingBorderInput, GradientIconFill,FlexRow,Subtitle
} from './StyledComp';

const dummyData = {
  title: "Sample Project",
  websiteLink: "http://example.com",
  githubLink: "http://github.com/sample",
  demoLink: "http://youtube.com/watch?v=demo",
  description: "This is a sample project description. It explains the purpose and functionality of the project in brief.",
  demonstration: [
    {
      description: "Step 1: User Registration",
      gifImage: "path/to/registration-demo.gif"
    },
    {
      description: "Step 2: User Login and Dashboard Overview",
      gifImage: "path/to/login-demo.gif"
    }
  ]
};

const Project = () => {
  const { title, websiteLink, githubLink, demoLink, description, demonstration } = dummyData;

  return (
    <GradientBackground startColor="#6B73FF" endColor="#000DFF">
      <Card>
        <ProjectContainer>
          <FlexRow>
            <GradientText startColor="#FF7A7A" endColor="#FF3D68"><TextMod size="2.5rem" font="Verdana, sans-serif" weight="bold">{title}</TextMod></GradientText>
            <FloatingElement>
              <CircleExpand>🔵</CircleExpand>
            </FloatingElement>
          </FlexRow>

          <HoverGradientShift startColor="#FF7A7A" endColor="#FF3D68" hoverStartColor="#00FF00" hoverEndColor="#0000FF">
            "Hover over me!"
          </HoverGradientShift>

        

          <GradientContainer startColor="#FF7A7A" endColor="#FF3D68">
            <LinksContainer>
              <GradientButton href={websiteLink}>Website</GradientButton>
              <GradientButton href={githubLink}>GitHub</GradientButton>
              {demoLink && <GradientButton href={demoLink}>Demonstration</GradientButton>}
            </LinksContainer>
          </GradientContainer>

          <LinePulse lineColor="#333" />
          <GlowingLine lineColor="#FF7A7A" shadowColor="#FF3D68" />
          <GrowVerticalLine lineColor="#333" />
          <GrowHorizontalLine lineColor="#333" />

          <GlassCard>
            <Description>
              <TextMod size="1.2rem" color="#444" font="Verdana, sans-serif" weight="500" decoration="underline">
                <LineHeightText lineHeight="1.6">{description}</LineHeightText>
              </TextMod>
            </Description>
          </GlassCard>

          {demonstration && (
            <DemonstrationContainer>
              <GlassCard>
                <Subtitle>Demonstration:</Subtitle>
                <StepsContainer>
                  {demonstration.map((step, index) => (
                    <StepItem key={index}>
                      <StepDescription>
                        <TextMod type="italic">{step.description}</TextMod>
                      </StepDescription>
                      <GifContainer>
                        <GifImage src={step.gifImage} alt={`Demo for step ${index + 1}`} />
                      </GifContainer>
                    </StepItem>
                  ))}
                </StepsContainer>
              </GlassCard>
            </DemonstrationContainer>
          )}
        </ProjectContainer>
      </Card>
      <GradientIconFill>🌟</GradientIconFill>
      <ExpandingBorderInput placeholder="Type here..." />
    </GradientBackground>
  );
};

export default Project;
